OL,3,CRyanair mulls larger staff bonus for
OL,4,Ccatching passengers with oversized
OL,5,Cluggage
OL,7,FPassengers are charged a fee of up to
OL,8,F75 euros (#65) for bringing luggage
OL,9,Fthat is larger than they paid for
OL,10,Fwhile booking their journey.
OL,12,FRyanair currently includes a small
OL,13,Fcarry-on bag ` capped at a size of
OL,14,F40x20x25cm and weight of 10kg ` with
OL,15,Fevery ticket, which is usually the
OL,16,Fsize of a medium backpack and goes
OL,17,Fbeneath the seat.
OL,19,FThey have recently announced that this
OL,20,Fwill soon be increased to 40x30x20cm.
