OL,5,Cluggage
OL,7,FPassengers must pay a fee if they want
OL,8,Fto bring larger luggage or if they
OL,9,Fwant to bring multiple bags.
OL,11,FSpeaking to the business news on RTE's
OL,12,FMorning Ireland, Ryanair boss Michael
OL,13,FO'Leary said: "We're flying largely
OL,14,Ffull flights, about half the
OL,15,Fpassengers can bring two bags and the
OL,16,Fother half can only bring one `
OL,17,Fbecause that's all that fits in the
OL,18,Fplane.
OL,20,F"We're already struggling with that
OL,21,Famount of baggage.
