OL,5,Cluggage
OL,7,F"That's one of the reasons we are so
OL,8,Faggressive about eliminating the
OL,9,Fscourge of passengers with excess
OL,10,Fbaggage."
OL,12,FMr O'Leary said more than 99.9% of
OL,13,Fpassengers comply with baggage rules,
OL,14,Fwith "sizers" located within the
OL,15,Fairport.
OL,17,FHe said: "We are happy to incentivise
OL,18,Four (staff) with a share of those
OL,19,Fexcess baggage fees, which we think
OL,20,Fwill decline over the coming year or
OL,21,Ftwo."
