OL,7,FThe chief executive added: "It is
OL,8,Fabout 1.50 euro per bag ` and we're
OL,9,Fthinking of increasing it, so we
OL,10,Feliminate it."
OL,12,FMembers of the European Parliament are
OL,13,Fpushing for airlines to allow
OL,14,Fpassengers to be allowed to bring an
OL,15,Fon-board personal item and small hand
OL,16,Fluggage f
OL,18,FHowever, Mr O'Leary predicted the
OL,19,Fproposal will not come into law due to
OL,20,Fa lack of space.
